        <briefdescription>
<para>Set the device hostname postfix. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Convert the hostname postfix to hexadecimal value and set the device hostname with the converted value. This is only used if CONFIG_NET_HOSTNAME_UNIQUE is set.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>hostname_postfix</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Usually link address. The function will convert this to a hexadecimal string. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>postfix_len</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Length of the hostname_postfix array.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>0 if ok, &lt;0 if error </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
